@startuml referral-states
title Referral ServiceRequest status, driven by Task events
hide empty description

state "on-hold" as onhold
state "entered-in-error" as eie

[*] --> active : created (status = active)
active --> onhold : returned for revision
onhold --> active : resubmitted with a new approval Task
active --> completed : final approval / fulfilment Task completed
active --> revoked : cancelled, or a commission Task failed / rejected
onhold --> revoked : cancelled
active --> eie : correction
completed --> [*]
revoked --> [*]
eie --> [*]

note bottom of active
  An SLA breach sets only Task.businessStatus = overdue;
  the ServiceRequest status does not change.
end note
@enduml
